Package com.clarkparsia.common.base

This package defines a set of classes primarily working with Java core objects or other basic operations.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Copyable<T> Interface for an object that can be copied.
FileSupplier Interface for something that supplies a file.
ThrowingSupplier<T,E extends Exception> A class that can supply instances of a particular type.

Copyables Utility methods for copying collections of Copyable objects.
DataKey<E>  
DataMap An object that maps keys to values in a type-safe manner.

FormattingResourceBundle Simple extension to ResourceBundle that handles message formatting via MessageFormat for values in the resource bundle.

Functions2.Strings String based functions.
HashCodeUtil Collected methods which allow easy implementation of hashCode.
ImmutableOptions Deprecated. Use Options.unmodifiable(Options) instead

Bool Three-valued (true, false, unknown) boolean type.
 

Package com.clarkparsia.common.base Description

This package defines a set of classes primarily working with Java core objects or other basic operations. Many are a supplement to what is found in Guava.
